Sonic49 | ??? 24-May-21 12:10 PM
G r e e n. This place is nice. No direct sunlight comes in here besides through the window that makes up one of the walls, giving the place a not-so-greenhouse-y feel. The lights here seem to be a bit... different to compensate for the lack of sunlight at the very least, although it's not really too different from the rest of the place (it just feels off). There are, however, tons of plants here. That's nice. Fruits, veggies, poisons... all of them seem to be here in some fashion, each clearly labeled with what they are. And the air in this room is rather fresh. You wonder how the plants get their water, especially since there's no hose here, but that doesn't matter much. (edited)

As long as he can be there for others… being lumberjack may not do much in his eyes, but being there for others… does wonders. “I… I can help…. I can be there… for others… be peoples crutch… I can…” He murmured. But a sudden feeling made his skin crawl. Like something slithering up his legs.
